query:
UPDATE inventory i
INNER JOIN warehouseLocations wl ON i.locationId = wl.id
SET i.tenantId = 1
WHERE wl.code IN ('Z01-01-01', 'Z01-01-02', 'Z01-01-03', 'Z01-01-04');
